node.text:
What is the meaning of life? Hell if we know, but here are some helpful pointers for staying #EverydayReady as you return to your everyday life this summer.
•
Brought to you in partnership with the @uscca, the Everyday Ready series focuses on tips, tricks, and advice to keep your summer adventures from making the evening news.

node.text: SWAT officer, Special Forces instructor, and close quarters combat expert @jaredwihongi has over 35 years of martial arts experience and 21 years of law enforcement experience. node.text: If you're being pursued by a hostile drone, you'd better have someone riding shotgun 💥

node.accessibility_caption: Our Norris Sneaker in Navy Blue.

node.text: Casual comfort, tactical build—the Norris Sneaker is now available in two new colors and a brand new low-cut version. Shop the Norris Sneaker collection now through the link in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Our Norris Sneaker in Navy Blue.
Our Norris Sneaker in black and white.
Our Norris Sneaker Low in Kangaroo.
Our Norris Sneaker Low in black.
A man wearing our Apex tactical cargo pant on a range.

node.text: Originally designed to allow tactical end-users to carry extra ammo while keeping a low profile, the added capacity and streamlined look of our Apex Pant quickly caught on for a multitude of other uses. Today, the Apex is a 5.11 favorite worn by everyone from tactical users and outdoor enthusiasts to photographers and movie directors. #AlwaysBeReady

node.accessibility_caption: A man wearing our Apex tactical cargo pant on a range.
A photographer wearing our Apex tactical cargo pant walking through a field carrying a DSLR Camera.
Photo by 5.11 Tactical on August 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: Own the initiative. When every second counts, your speed and decisiveness might just make the difference. #AlwaysBeReady

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 5.11 Tactical on August 16, 2021. May be an image of leather wallet.

node.text: The dark art of minimalism 🙌 Spare no space for excess anything. #AlwaysBeReady

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by 5.11 Tactical on August 15, 2021 tagging @leupoldoptics, and @timkennedymma. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Crisis doesn't care if you're lazy, weak, or weary. It preys on the complacent who can't be bothered to #AlwaysBeReady

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 5.11 Tactical on August 14, 2021. May be an image of knife.

node.text: Which is mightier? 🗡️ 🖊️
